# Changelog

[2.0.0]

⚠️ BREAKING CHANGES

* Pure ESM Migration: This package is now ESM-only. CJS (CommonJS) support has been dropped.

* Package now is ESM-only - type `module`.

* Minimal Node version: `22.18.0`.

Changed

* NPM Distribution: Updated the build process to ensure the NPM registry only contains the ES Module (ESM) version of the library.

### [1.0.1] (2023-04-17)

* Code cleanup

### [1.0.0] (2021-10-06)

### Features

* Initial release
